window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The end is near, I can feel it in my bones.</p> <p>Secrets are practically seeping from the seams of this fabricated society.</p> <p>Deceiving you with the pretty allure of all that is promised.</p> <p>Descending you into the inky black reality of this world’s past, present and future.</p> <p>If we can all survive, what kind of future awaits us. Forever servants to the tyrants that have ruled Salem for over three hundred years?</p> <p>What if the history books got it wrong, though?</p> <p>What if the past isn’t what it seems?</p> <p>What if it can help us rewrite the future?</p> <p>The casket is closing, we’re running out of time.</p> <p>No matter which way this goes, it’s going to be someone’s Demise.</p>"; 
